com.netflix.governator

Class LifecycleInjectorCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.governator.LifecycleInjectorCreator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InjectorCreator<LifecycleInjector>

    public class LifecycleInjectorCreator
extends java.lang.Object
implements InjectorCreator<LifecycleInjector>
    Custom strategy for creating a Guice Injector that enables support for lifecycle annotations such as @PreDestroy and @PostConstruct as well as injector lifecycle hooks via the LifecycleListener API. The LifecycleInjectorCreator may be overridden to handle pre-create and post-create notification.
